The paper discusses sparse estimation methods and their application in various fields such as unsupervised and supervised learning. These topics are commonly found in the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), information theory (cs.IT), and numerical analysis (cs.NA). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
